messages.text: I’m in hospital. Mom had a kidney failure.
Oh god! How is she?
it’s serious. But the doctors say she’s stable now
she wants to see you
I’ll be home in a few days
I knew you’d say that
did you tell her where I am?
I told her you’re on a business trip to California
good. Tell her I’m thinking about her
if you can come home earlier than planned,  please do
okay
what are you doing now?
I’m in the guest room at Isaiah’s house.
someone is picking me up soon to bring me to that job
actually the butler has just knocked on my door
let me know what happens
an hour later
he brought me to a place called the House of Correction
what is it?
a house
and?
I’m waiting in the hall to be told what to do
this is so weird. There is a mirror in front of me
and there is a woman in the mirror
what?
apparently she’s the Righteous Lady.
Some minor goddess supposed to watch over female behaviour.
female behaviour?
modesty, chastity, all that shit
it actually looks like she’s a living person inside the mirror.  It’s scary
it must be some optical illusion. They’re playing with your mind
I’m sure they are
okay he told me to go inside a room. ‘A sinful woman is waiting for me’.
sinful in what sense?
she kissed her cousin while she was married to her half-brother
married to her half-brother!!
oh god I feel so bad for her
why is she so scared? :O
well… I’m supposed to punish her
with that thing you showed me yesterday??
yeah…
Sean NO!!
I can’t just stand here and do nothing
you’re not a bad person
I’m not, but I have to play the game
find an excuse, say you’re not ready for this yet
if I don’t do it someone else will
at least it won’t be you!!
I can’t talk right now
Sean!!!
two hours later
it’s over
what happened?
I did what I had to do
I can’t believe this.
I can’t believe I’m talking to my brother
sorry?
my brother would not beat to death an innocent woman!
I didn’t beat her to death!!!
I didn’t even hurt her that much. Just a couple of bruises.
she’ll be fine in no time
are you sure?
I’m sick of your suspicions Cal. You should have a little trust in me.
I HAD to do what they asked. But the woman WILL BE FINE
alright. I still think you’re acting weird
it’s like you’re a different person
what exactly are you thinking?
that someone stole my phone?
happy?
right, okay, fine.
whatever.
a little bit later
Sean…
what?
Mom died
when?? How??
ten minutes ago. Her body suddenly shut down.
was she in pain?
I don’t think so. It was very gentle
I wish I could have said goodbye…
she said something about you before she died…
this isn’t easy…
Cal you’re scaring me!
she said that we don’t have the same father
what does that mean?
well… Dad is only my dad
what the hell are you saying??
who’s my father?
I don’t know. She didn’t tell me
what?!
I asked her but she was dying!
she could hardly speak anymore
she just said: dangerous
my father is dangerous?
I don’t know, maybe.
why should I believe this?
she probably had no idea what she was saying
she did. She was clear-minded until the very end
I know this is terrible for you...
but it actually makes sense if you think about it
you looked nothing like Dad…
and he’s always treated me differently than you.
that’s not true
you never noticed because you were the favourite son
come on Sean, let’s not dredge up childhood conflicts now
I’m not trying to. I’m just saying you’re right. It is possible.
Mum said she had you the same year she met Dad.
Don’t you think that’s a bit strange?
she wasn’t the kind of woman who would sleep with a guy she just met.
The opposite rather
she must have been already pregnant.
and she was so vague about her life before us.
All we knew was that she came from Wyoming and her family was dead.
how could they all be dead?
I think there’s more to it.
how’s that?
she said she had me when she was 20.
you know what, to me she’s always looked a lot younger than she claimed
she looked young that’s true…
but okay so… what’s your theory?
I’m not sure. I feel a bit confused right now.
I need a moment to myself
of course
a little bit later
Sean!!
I have bad news
what?
my wedding has been anticipated to the day after tomorrow!!
shit
we need to go!
I wanted to stay here a little longer, I’ve still got work to do
we have to go now!!
we said I’d stay two weeks. I’ll take you away in a few days.
no please!!
what’s the problem with that?
the wedding night…
oh
Mother explained to me what’s going to happen
I can’t…
sorry I didn’t think of that
we’ll leave before the wedding
thank you!!!
how should we do this? You know best
everybody in my home goes to sleep by 11
I’ll sneak out at midnight
meet you at 12:15 at the edge of town, under the oak.
okay, but not tonight
why not tonight??
tomorrow night. I want one more day here.
